We simulated DNMs for genes under the mTADA model in Table 1. All 19,538 genes and their mutation rates from our current real dataset were used. A gene was assigned to one of the four groups (four models) by using the probability (π0, π1, π2, π3). We used \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
